With spring in full bloom and blue skies ahead, Bergdorf Goodman Fashion Director @lindafargo walks us through the season's latest trends along with all the new arrivals we have in store at 5th Avenue and 58th Street. Whether it's romantic silhouettes from go-to brands like @khaite_ny and @zimmermann, bold hues from @driesvannoten, sustainable selections from @stellamccartney and @studiooneeightynine, or must-haves from @prada, the Spring collections have one thing in common—optimism. As Fargo says, "This season I feel very uplifted and I know if I walked down the street in any of these pieces I would have a positive effect on other people." Discover these looks and more from the Spring 2021 collections now in store and online at BG.com.

